Excellent ability to communicate messaging security solutions towards the customer</li>
<li>
Strong understanding of the security market place</li>
<li>
Previous experience in a customer-facing organization selling or delivering services to operators</li>
<li>
Must be able to develop a strong working relationship with CSO, Messaging and Network organizations</li>
<li>
Proactive actions and thinking</li>
